headline: Trump: Conflict About Ron DeSantis Is ‘Totally Fake News’
sentences: I think Ron said last week, he said it very publicly, he said, 'The press is never going to get in the middle of my friendship with Donald Trump.
Ron wanted to run and I endorsed him, and that helped him greatly and he went on and he's done a really terrific job in Florida.
No, I have a very good relationship with Ron and intend to have it for a long time."
You know, Ron has been very good, he's been a friend of mine for a long time.
He was right up front along with Jim Jordan and all the rest of them.
The Republicans really stuck together, and it was a great thing.
I thought it was very interesting, actually, and very nice.
But he said that, and I agree with him on that 100%.

EXCERPT:
TRUMP: "I get along great with Ron.
Ron was very good on the Mueller hoax.
We are not going to do that stuff.'
